item.title: CVE-2017-2752|2024-08-05T14:02:07.683Z -- tommy%20hilfiger -- tommy%20hilfiger%20th24%2F7%20android%20app
item.description: A potential security vulnerability caused by incomplete obfuscation of application configuration information was discovered in Tommy Hilfiger TH24/7 Android app versions 2.0.0.11, 2.0.1.14, 2.1.0.16, and 2.2.0.19. HP has no access to customer data as a result of this issue.
